The '''Librarian's Assembly''',<ref name="CSWE">{{CSWECite|II|253|Librarian's Assembly}}</ref><ref name="DB" /> also known as the '''Librarians' Assembly''',<ref name="TNEGtC">''[[The New Essential Guide to Characters]]''</ref><ref name="JvS">[[Jedi vs. Sith: The Essential Guide to the Force (real-life book)|''Jedi vs. Sith: The Essential Guide to the Force'']]</ref> the '''Librarians Assembly''',<ref name="TJP" /> or the '''Librarian Assembly''',<ref name="PotJS">''[[Power of the Jedi Sourcebook]]''</ref> was an organization of [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Lore Keeper]]s based in the [[Jedi Temple/Legends|Jedi Temple]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. Tasked with overseeing the collection of data and its filing within the [[Jedi Archives/Legends|Temple Archives]], it reported directly to the [[Council of First Knowledge/Legends|Council of First Knowledge]].<ref name="TJP" />

